Forms :--

1. vital to business applications --> login, submit, register etc.
2. create an experience that guides the user efficiently and effectively through the workflow.

3. Developers :--
   
   1. Data binding
   2. Chnage tracking
   3. validation
   4. visual feedback
   5. Error messages.
   6. Form submission.

4. 1. Template - collect data
   2. Class -Bind data
   3. Service - Send data
   4. server.

5. Two approches : --
 
 1. Templte driven forms -- Heavy on the component template.
 2. Reactive forms  -- Heavy on the component class.